		<category scheme="http://blog.8-p.info/2009" term="Uncategorized" /><category scheme="http://blog.8-p.info/2009" term="lang-en" />		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[Hatena released &#8220;Hatena Bookmark for iPhone&#8221;. Great!
